          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price was calculated from the Department of Primary Industries NSW  2012 NSW Gross margin, Department of Primary Industries NSW, “Canola After Pasture, Dryland Winter 2012, Gross Margin Budget”. The prices were converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.AUD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2023-06-01) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
        </property>
